    <style id="node-bootstrap-server-classes">
  body {
    transition: background-color .5s;
  }

  .initial-node-bootstrap-server-loader {
    z-index: 8888888;
    width: 106px;
    height: 112px;
    position: fixed;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    opacity: 1;
    transition: opacity .5s linear;
  }

  .initial-node-bootstrap-server-loader-leaving {
    transition: opacity .5s linear;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .svg-loader {
    --first-stroke-length: 314;
    --third-stroke-length: 314;
  }

  .svg-loader-circle1 {
    stroke-dasharray: 314;
    stroke-dashoffset: 314;
    stroke-dasharray: var(--first-stroke-length);
    stroke-dashoffset: var(--first-stroke-length);

    /*   https://easings.net easeInOutQuint */
    -webkit-animation: firstCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.86, 0, 0.07, 1) infinite;
    animation: firstCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.86, 0, 0.07, 1) infinite;
  }

  .svg-loader-circle2 {
    fill: #1D28FA;
    fill: var(--cp-color-app-primary, #a3a3a3);
    /*   https://easings.net easeInCirc */
    -webkit-animation: secondCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.6, 0.04, 0.98, 0.335) infinite;
    animation: secondCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.6, 0.04, 0.98, 0.335) infinite;
    transition: fill 350ms linear;
  }

  .svg-loader-circle3 {
    stroke-dasharray: 314;
    stroke-dashoffset: 314;
    stroke-dasharray: var(--third-stroke-length);
    stroke-dashoffset: var(--third-stroke-length);

    /*   https://easings.net easeOutCirc */
    -webkit-animation: thirdCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.075, 0.82, 0.165, 1) infinite;
    animation: thirdCircle 3.5s cubic-bezier(0.075, 0.82, 0.165, 1) infinite;
  }

  .svg-loader-circle1,.svg-loader-circle3 {
    stroke: #1D28FA;
    stroke: var(--cp-color-app-primary, #a3a3a3);
    transition: stroke 350ms linear;
  }

  @keyframes firstCircle {
    0% {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
    37% {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke-dashoffset: 314;
      stroke-dashoffset: var(--first-stroke-length);
    }
    37.01% {
      opacity: 0;
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
    99.98% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    99.99% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
    }
  }

  @keyframes secondCircle {
    0% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    37% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
      ry: 10;
    }
    55% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(200px);
      ry: 25;
    }
    55.01% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    99.99% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes thirdCircle {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      stroke-dashoffset: 314;
      stroke-dashoffset: var(--third-stroke-length);
    }
    54.99% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    55% {
      opacity: 1;
      stroke-dashoffset: 314;
      stroke-dashoffset: var(--third-stroke-length);
    }
    93% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      opacity: 1;
    }
    99.99% {
      stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 0;
      stroke-dashoffset: 314;
      stroke-dashoffset: var(--third-stroke-length);
    }
  }
</style>
